to the editor re fbi knew for years about terror pilot training front page may 18 the assertion that the fbi had largely failed to draw together evidence gathered piecemeal over the years and had failed to share its findings can bring nothing but benefit to our nation if all of us from president bush and the leadership of the democratic party on down view that claim of a lack of coordination not as an opportunity for stonewalling or attacking the republican party but rather as an occasion for assessing and improving the level of america 's home defenses that is something that all intelligent patriots desire michael wagner brooklyn may 18 2002

